text: The Wonderful Wizard of Oz is a 1910 American silent fantasy movie directed by Otis Turner and was based on the 1900 novel of the same name by L. Frank Baum. It stars Bebe Daniels and the movie is currently in archive. ==Other websites== * * Category:1910 movies Category:1910s fantasy movies Category:American fantasy movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Otis Turner Category:Movies about wizards Category:Movies set in Kansas
